    "originContent": "**禁用英雄**配置页面与**选用英雄**配置页面基本一致，仅在右上角多了切换模式的按钮，点击按钮可以切换禁用模式。",
    "translatedContent": "**Disabled Heroes** configuration page is basically the same as the **Selected Heroes** configuration page, with an additional mode switch button in the upper right corner. Clicking the button can switch to the disable mode."
  },
