    "translatedContent": "> To add or update a hero’s rune configuration on the **Rune Configuration Page**, you need to select and save a rune page in the game client’s **Collection - Runes**, then change the summoner spells from the top right and press the **Add Configuration** button or the *Update current game configuration to this config* button in the rune configuration item to add or update the rune setup."
